Cheap food with decent quality

I picked number 4 on order ticket. The traditional is good, I can taste the smell of ginger and crunchy peanuts. Signature rice noodle is good, and sufficient volume. 

But the soy sauce chicken is just so so. 

Will come again if pass by.
